An ubuntu indicator
keep your computer in safey while you leave for a short time ---- prevent the thief to steal you computer

Function:
1.The app listen to the ac-adapter and the computer lid if they were pulled out or closed up
2.If the ac-adapter catch the signal above,the computer will play an alarm music or use your own music 

Optional Function:
1.send you a message to alarm your computer is in danger (the script sendmessage.sh just used for china location)
2.capture the thief's face and upload to anywhere you want (default to Dropbox)
*You can write any optional function to alarm
